      "title": "NTMI to remain closed on Fridays and Saturdays",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Transport Medical Institute (NTMI) says its services are not provided on Fridays and Saturdays until further notice.",
        "According to its director Dr. Savindra Gamage, the NTMI will limit services from the 01st of July.",
        "However, the general public can schedule an appointment by contacting the hotline 1225, visiting the institute\u2019s official website (www.ntmi.lk) or via e-channeling from Monday to Thursday."
      ],
